sentences: A..C..O (born February 3, 1977) is a Japanese singer.
She made her debut in 1995 with the pop single "Fuan nano" (不安なの).
In 2003, after a two-year hiatus, she enlisted the help of the avant-garde audio-visual performance group portable [k]ommunity for her quieter, more delicate album, Irony.
AllMusic described Irony as "one of the most beautiful albums to come out of Japan in 2003", with the music compared to an "airy lullaby".
